---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import { Carousel } from "../../components/Carousel.jsx";
import i18n from '../../data/sidebar.json'; // <-- Import the data file

// Detect language and get the correct text
const currentPath = Astro.url.pathname;
const lang = currentPath.startsWith('/es') ? 'es' : currentPath.startsWith('/fr') ? 'fr' : 'en';
const t = i18n[lang];

const gbsSlides = [
  {
    title: "What is Guillain-Barré Syndrome?",
    content: `<div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed"><p>Guillain-Barré Syndrome (GBS) is a rare and serious autoimmune disorder where the body's immune system mistakenly attacks its own peripheral nerves—the network outside of the brain and spinal cord.</p><p>The onset is often sudden, escalating over hours or days into a neurological emergency. It is the leading cause of acute, non-trauma-related paralysis worldwide.</p></div>`,
  },
  {
    title: "A Case of Mistaken Identity",
    content: `<div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed"><p>The most accepted theory is <strong class="font-semibold text-gray-900">"molecular mimicry"</strong>. Often, the syndrome begins after a common infection, like a stomach bug (*Campylobacter jejuni*) or a respiratory virus.</p><p>The immune system creates antibodies to fight the germ, but some parts of the germ look remarkably similar to our own nerve cells. The antibodies make a catastrophic error and begin attacking the healthy nerves, leading to the weakness, numbness, and paralysis that define GBS.</p></div>`,
  },
  {
    title: "Hope on the Horizon",
    content: `<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">While current treatments help, they are not a cure and are not effective for everyone. This is why research is so critical. Scientists are working to find faster diagnostic tools and develop new, more targeted therapies. Your support helps fuel this vital research and brings hope to every person affected by GBS.</p>`,
  },
  // {
  //   title: "Impact on Nerve Cells",
  //   content: `<img src="/gbs-details.png" alt="Guillain-Barré Syndrome Explanation - Neuron and Nerve System" class="rounded-xl shadow-lg w-full object-cover" /><p class="mt-4 text-center text-sm text-gray-500">*Image illustrating the impact of GBS on nerve cells and pathways.</p>`,
  // },
];
---

<MainLayout title="About GBS">
  <div
    transition:name="about-gbs-card"
    class="m-4 md:m-8 lg:m-12 p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10 bg-white rounded-xl max-w-6xl w-full mx-auto text-gray-800 font-sans"
  >
    <div class="text-center">
      <h1
        class="font-display font-extrabold text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-gray-900"
      >
        What is Guillain-Barré Syndrome?
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg text-gray-500">
        Understanding the condition behind the challenge.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8">
      {/* Pass the translations object 't' as a prop */}
      <Carousel client:load slides={gbsSlides} i18n={t} />
    </div>

    <hr class="my-8 md:my-12 border-gray-200 w-48 mx-auto" />

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-center mb-8">
        Find Out More
      </h3>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div
          class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6 flex flex-col text-center"
        >
          <h4 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900">
            GBS|CIDP Foundation Int.
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2 flex-grow text-sm">
            The leading global nonprofit for supporting patients and funding
            research for GBS.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://www.gbs-cidp.org/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="mt-4 inline-block text-brand-blue font-semibold hover:underline"
          >
            Visit Website &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6 flex flex-col text-center"
        >
          <h4 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900">
            GBS|CIDP España
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2 flex-grow text-sm">
            A patient advocacy group based in Spain, providing support and
            resources.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://gbs-cidp.org.es/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-brand-blue font-semibold hover:underline"
          >
            Visit Website &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6 flex flex-col text-center"
        >
          <h4 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900">
            AFSGB & TSFN (France)
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2 flex-grow text-sm">
            The French association for Guillain-Barré Syndrome, providing
            information and support to patients in France.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://www.guillainbarre.fr/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-brand-blue font-semibold hover:underline"
          >
            Visiter le site web &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>